task.summary: Got the Dashboard working beautifully. Its quite awesome. Added CVCamera class for accessing a USB Camera. Logging and Dashboard modules are fully functional. Command will require on-robot testing. Vision Module testing is up next.
Made minor tweaks to various classes, and added other classes we have used in the past.
Refactored out explicit team references, fixed Command Implementation. Made Routers into commands that hack up the start method.
Removed zip file support from logger, update now creates a new file when called. Dont call update in periodic or you will have regrets.
Converted to Kotlin, began expansion of lib.
Added a ton of stuff, Including Robot Position Tracker.
Did some code cleanup, and added CommandDSL and WaitFor.
Finished adding pure pursuit code, fixed bug with default commands.
Initial release for v2.0, for 3309 use at champs.
Fix big oof of a bug ouch
Finished Commands V2 implementation, and removed commands v1. v2 is a much cleaner implementation with many more features.
removed broken motion stuff, fixed some small stuff.
